---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
---

<LegalLayout
    title="Refund Policy | Robgrappler"
    description="Robgrappler refund policy."
>
    <!-- Refunds -->
    <section
        id="refunds"
        class="page-section min-h-screen pt-24 pb-12 bg-brand-black"
    >
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl font-bebas text-brand-bone mb-8 border-b border-brand-gold pb-4"
            >
                <span class="lang-en">Refund Policy</span>
                <span class="lang-es hidden">Política de Reembolsos</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm text-gray-400">
                <p class="mb-4">
                    <span class="lang-en"
                        >Due to the digital nature of our content, we generally
                        do not offer refunds once a video has been downloaded or
                        streamed.</span
                    >
                    <span class="lang-es hidden"
                        >Debido a la naturaleza digital de nuestro contenido,
                        generalmente no ofrecemos reembolsos una vez que un
                        video ha sido descargado o reproducido.</span
                    >
                </p>
                <p>
                    <span class="lang-en"
                        >However, if you have a technical issue preventing
                        access, or if you accidentally purchased the same match
                        twice, contact us within 7 days.</span
                    >
                    <span class="lang-es hidden"
                        >Sin embargo, si tienes un problema técnico que impide
                        el acceso, o si compraste accidentalmente el mismo
                        combate dos veces, contáctanos dentro de los 7 días.</span
                    >
                </p>
            </div>
            <a
                href="/"
                data-track="footer_back_home"
                class="mt-8 inline-block text-brand-gold hover:text-white font-bold"
            >
                <span class="lang-en">&larr; Back to Home</span>
                <span class="lang-es hidden">&larr; Volver al Inicio</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</LegalLayout>
